        1268
      ],
      "content": "A device with a Silverlight-enabled web browser that you can use to access the websites where you'll  create Intune user accounts (the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Intune Account Portal<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>) and where you manage devices, groups, and policies  (the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Intune administration console<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>)."
